Package: lapacker
Type: Package
Title: The Missing 'LAPACKE' Interface for R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yi Pan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yi Pan <ypan1988@gmail.com>
Description: Provide the 'lapacke.h' header file for R. 'LAPACKE' is a
    collection of wrappers that provide a C interface to the FORTRAN 'LAPACK'
    library. Currently only the double precision / double complex 'LAPACK'
    routines are supported.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
